descriptionHtml:
Requiers ApachiiSkyHair http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
The two followers will be at the sleepin gaints inn at riverwood
The followers are good with destruction and conjuration magic and onehanded weapons and heavy armour. They are equipped with a daedric bow and arrows and with two daedric swords.
They know 4 conjuration spells and 2 destriction spells.
Conjuration: conjure all 3 atronachs and dremora lord
Destruction: fireball and wall of flames
 
To make the most of this mod you need three other mods 
one is this mod http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17026
the other is a better female texture http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812 (or any other one)
and a multi follower mod (any one you want)
